    J. Phys. Chem. C 2021, 125, 18380−18394
    https://doi.org/10.1021/acs.jpcc.1c01190
    - Developed to describe Mg/Al/Si/O interactions in S-glass and other magnesium 
        aluminosilicate (MAS) glass compositions. 
    - The training set includes the density functional theory data of the energy response 
        of various Mg/Al/Si/O crystals during volumetric expansion and compression and Mg 
        migration inside Mg/Al/Si/O crystals.


